heroSlider v0.1a

This is currently an alpha version of the plugin and should be considered unusable until a beta version is released.

Keep an eye on this page for a usable build.

Planned Features:

Customize Scrolling Times:
    Slide Delay            - Implemented
    Auto-scroll timeout    
    Auto-scroll disable    - Implemented
    Pause on hover disable

Customizable Transitions:
    Choose from default transitions for all slides
    
Visuals:
    Automatically added buttons                  - Implemented
    Automatically added "jump-to" bar
    Simple to modify css for customizing buttons - Implemented
    Enable or disable jump to slide bar
    Enable or disable buttons
    Responsive Sizing for hero unit              - Implemented
    Caption support and customizability
